WHEN YOU OPEN AN ACCOUNT
WITH THE BANK,

20:53.083 --> 20:54.083
THEY ACTUALLY WILL
GIVE YOU--

20:54.083 --> 20:56.050
GIVE YOU YOUR MONEY BACK?
(laughs)

20:56.050 --> 20:57.062
WILL GIVE YOU MONEY BACK.
THAT'S EXACTLY RIGHT.

20:57.062 --> 20:58.070
PAT, THAT'S ALL GOOD,

20:58.070 --> 21:00.052
BUT THERE'S A LITTLE BIT
OF A PROBLEM HERE.

21:00.052 --> 21:03.058
YOU GOTTA GET HUGE DISTRIBUTION.
YOU GOTTA BUY YOUR WAY IN.

21:03.058 --> 21:04.073
THIS IS WHAT DAYMOND WAS
TALKING ABOUT.

21:04.073 --> 21:07.063
YOU NEED MILLIONS OF DOLLARS,
SO...

21:07.063 --> 21:11.082
SO I PUT OUT ONE PRESS RELEASE
ON THIS PRODUCT.

21:11.082 --> 21:15.047
THIS PRODUCT EXPLODED
WORLDWIDE.

21:15.047 --> 21:17.052
IT'S IN POLAND, CROATIA,
CHINA--

21:17.052 --> 21:18.053
$50,000 IN SALES.

21:18.053 --> 21:20.067
$50,000 IN SALES IS NOT
AN EXPLOSION.

21:20.067 --> 21:21.070
IT IS IN CROATIA.

21:21.070 --> 21:22.080
UH, IT'S AN IMPLOSION.

21:22.080 --> 21:24.062
BUT IT'S
A VERY UNIQUE PRODUCT, RIGHT?

21:24.062 --> 21:26.062
THE--YOU BUY THIS PRODUCT
BECAUSE OF THE NAME,

21:26.062 --> 21:28.052
AND YOU COME BACK
BECAUSE OF THE FRAGRANCE.

21:28.052 --> 21:31.042
(Daymond) THIS BUSINESS
IS SOLELY ON ADVERTISING,

21:31.042 --> 21:33.047
AND $100,000
WILL ONLY BUY YOU

21:33.047 --> 21:36.057
ONE PAGE IN ONE OF THE BOOKS
THAT THE BIG GUYS ARE IN.

21:36.057 --> 21:39.065
PAT, HOW MUCH MONEY DO YOU HAVE
LEFT TO PUT IN THIS BUSINESS?

21:39.065 --> 21:40.082
FRANKLY I DON'T--

21:40.082 --> 21:42.053
I REALLY DON'T WANT TO PUT
ANY MORE MONEY INTO IT.

21:42.053 --> 21:44.043
SO THIS IS
YOUR BIG PLAY HERE.

21:44.043 --> 21:47.040
YOU GOTTA WALK OUT OF THE TANK
WITH THE CASH IN YOUR POCKET.

21:44.043 --> 21:47.040
ABSOLUTELY.

21:47.040 --> 21:48.053
CORRECT. THIS IS IT.

21:48.053 --> 21:49.078
(Daymond)
SO WHY WOULD YOU OFFER US...

21:48.053 --> 21:49.078
THIS--

21:49.078 --> 21:51.078
5%...

21:49.078 --> 21:51.078
RIGHT.

21:51.078 --> 21:53.067
FOR $100,000?

21:53.067 --> 21:54.077
THAT MEANS YOU ARE SAYING

21:54.077 --> 21:57.078
THE VALUE OF YOUR COMPANY
IS $2 MILLION.

21:57.078 --> 22:00.037
WELL, I'M GONNA GO BACK
TO MY POINT.

22:00.037 --> 22:01.070
YOU'RE TALKING
ABOUT A $32 BILLION MARKET.

22:01.070 --> 22:03.073
SEVEN OUT OF TEN ARE
FOR GIFTS.

22:03.073 --> 22:05.082
PAT, YOU'VE BROKE--YOU'VE BROKEN
THE CARDINAL RULE FOR ME.

22:05.082 --> 22:07.053
YEAH.

22:07.053 --> 22:09.077
WHEN SOMEONE STARTS OFF WITH,
"THE MARKET IS BILLIONS,

22:09.077 --> 22:12.053
AND IF I ONLY GET
A SMALL PERCENTAGE..."

22:09.077 --> 22:12.053
YEAH.

22:12.053 --> 22:13.062
I'LL BE OKAY."

22:13.062 --> 22:15.043
THAT'S ALWAYS A RED FLAG...

22:13.062 --> 22:15.043
RIGHT. RIGHT.

22:15.043 --> 22:16.067
BECAUSE YOU DON'T HAVE
ENOUGH CONFIDENCE

22:16.067 --> 22:18.062
IN YOUR PRODUCT TO DIVE
ALL-IN.

22:18.062 --> 22:19.077
NOW THAT'S NOT FAIR, MARK.

22:19.077 --> 22:21.075
THAT'S NOT FAIR.

22:19.077 --> 22:21.075
WHAT? I DON'T CARE.

22:21.075 --> 22:23.052
IF Y-YOU WANT MY MONEY,
AND YOU WANT

22:23.052 --> 22:24.072
A $2 MILLION VALUATION...

22:23.052 --> 22:24.072
RIGHT. RIGHT.

22:24.072 --> 22:27.073
AND IF YOU DON'T BELIEVE
ENOUGH TO SELL MONEY,

22:27.073 --> 22:29.077
THEN YOU'RE A WANT-REPRENEUR, NOT AN ENTREPRENEUR,

22:29.077 --> 22:31.063
AND FOR THAT REASON,
I'M OUT.

22:33.058 --> 22:36.048
NOW YOU SAID,
MONEY CAN'T BUY YOU HAPPINESS.

22:36.048 --> 22:37.048
I'VE BEEN RICH,
AND I'VE BEEN POOR.

22:37.048 --> 22:38.048
RIGHT.

22:38.048 --> 22:39.048
RICH IS BETTER.

22:39.048 --> 22:40.058
I AGREE.

22:40.058 --> 22:42.047
BY THE WAY,
IS THIS REAL MONEY?

22:42.047 --> 22:43.047
THAT IS REAL MONEY.

22:43.047 --> 22:44.065
WHAT?

22:43.047 --> 22:44.065
IT IS?

22:44.065 --> 22:45.073
AREN'T YOU GOING TO JAIL
FOR CHOPPING UP MONEY, PAT?

22:45.073 --> 22:47.037
WOW. THAT'S NOT RIGHT.

22:45.073 --> 22:47.037
(chuckles) YEAH.

22:47.037 --> 22:48.065
YEAH, THAT'S ACTUAL
SHREDDED U.S. CURRENCY.

22:48.065 --> 22:49.075
WHERE'D YOU GET IT FROM?

22:49.075 --> 22:51.068
I BUY THAT FROM
THE DEPARTMENT OF TREASURY.

22:51.068 --> 22:53.048
WELL, THAT'S COOL.

22:53.048 --> 22:55.060
IS THERE A BUSINESS IN TAPING
THIS BACK TOGETHER AGAIN?

22:55.060 --> 22:56.067
(sharks laugh)

22:55.060 --> 22:56.067
(chuckles) NO, THERE ISN'T.

22:56.067 --> 22:57.077
I DON'T KNOW.

22:57.077 --> 22:59.047
NO, THAT WOULD BE ILLEGAL.

22:57.077 --> 22:59.047
WE CAN'T DO THAT.

22:59.047 --> 23:01.050
LOOK, PAT, THE ONLY THING
OF VALUE I SEE IS THAT YOU--

23:01.050 --> 23:03.037
YOU'VE GOT THE NAME "MONEY"
IN THE FRAGRANCE CATEGORY.

23:03.037 --> 23:05.077
GOOD FOR YOU.
EVERYTHING ELSE IS INSANE.

23:05.077 --> 23:08.043
I LOVE MONEY.

23:08.043 --> 23:11.038
I'M EMOTIONALLY INVOLVED
WITH IT, AND IT LOVES ME, TOO,

23:11.038 --> 23:14.062
SO IT REALLY BREAKS MY HEART
TO HAVE TO SAY THIS TO YOU,

23:14.062 --> 23:16.072
BUT I'M OUT.

23:22.073 --> 23:26.068
I KNOW THAT 75% OF ALL
FRAGRANCES ARE SOLD DUTY-FREE,

23:26.068 --> 23:29.078
AND THE REST,
YOU NEED BACKING.

23:29.078 --> 23:33.042
I LIKE
THAT IDEA OF THE LICENSE...

23:34.043 --> 23:35.080
SO...

23:35.080 --> 23:39.050
I'LL GIVE YOU
THE $100,000 FOR 80%...

23:40.070 --> 23:42.073
AND I'LL GO LICENSE THE NAME,

23:42.073 --> 23:45.067
AND WE'LL MAKE A LOT
OF REAL MONEY.

23:45.067 --> 23:47.075
I-I THINK 80% IS--
IS QUITE HIGH.

23:47.075 --> 23:49.080
(Mark) JUST REMEMBER,

23:49.080 --> 23:52.068
100% OF NOTHING IS
STILL NOTHING.

23:52.068 --> 23:55.063
20% OF SOMETHING GROWING
AND BIG...

23:55.063 --> 23:58.052
HE'S OFFERING TO PUT HIMSELF
TO WORK FOR YOU

23:58.052 --> 23:59.057
AND PAY YOU TO DO IT.

23:59.057 --> 24:01.063
THAT NEVER HAPPENS.

24:02.077 --> 24:05.055
PAT, I MUST SAY, I THINK
YOUR PACKAGING IS GREAT.

24:05.055 --> 24:06.067
THANK YOU.

24:05.055 --> 24:06.067
PERFECT, OKAY?

24:06.067 --> 24:08.053
BUT THAT DOESN'T SMELL
LIKE MONEY TO ME.

24:08.053 --> 24:09.063
YOU KNOW WHAT?

24:09.063 --> 24:11.063
I GET $500 A WEEK OUT
OF THAT CASH MACHINE,

24:11.063 --> 24:13.058
'CAUSE THEY ALWAYS
GIVE IT TO ME IN NEW $50s...

24:11.063 --> 24:13.058
RIGHT. RIGHT.

24:13.058 --> 24:14.073
SO I PURPOSELY DO IT.

24:13.058 --> 24:14.073
YES.

24:14.073 --> 24:15.082
I ALWAYS SMELL THE MONEY
BEFORE I PUT IT

24:15.082 --> 24:17.038
IN MY WALLET...

24:15.082 --> 24:17.038
RIGHT.

24:17.038 --> 24:18.062
SO I REALLY KNOW
WHAT MONEY SMELLS LIKE.

24:18.062 --> 24:21.035
IT'S SUBTLE.
THIS IS NOT SUBTLE.

24:21.035 --> 24:22.045
EVEN THOUGH YOU LOOK
LIKE ROBERT REDFORD...

24:22.045 --> 24:23.045
(laughs)

24:23.045 --> 24:25.083
I'M OUT.

24:25.083 --> 24:27.073
(Daymond) YOU HAVE AN OFFER
ON THE TABLE.

24:30.060 --> 24:32.045
(sighs)

24:32.045 --> 24:34.038
80% OF THE COMPANY?

24:34.038 --> 24:35.040
YES.

24:36.083 --> 24:40.043
I MEAN, I REALLY WOULD LIKE
TO HAVE CONTROL OF THIS COMPANY.

24:40.043 --> 24:45.070
PAT, IT DISTURBS ME A LITTLE BIT
THAT WE HAD TO SHOW YOU

24:45.070 --> 24:48.055
THE OBVIOUS PATH,
WHICH WAS LICENSING.

24:48.055 --> 24:50.053
I DON'T THINK THIS IS
A PERFUME PRODUCT.

24:50.053 --> 24:52.050
I THINK THIS IS
A LICENSING PRODUCT.

24:52.050 --> 24:53.075
I DON'T SMELL THE MONEY.

24:53.075 --> 24:57.040
I SMELL FAILURE WITH
THE STRATEGY YOU HAVE TODAY,

24:57.040 --> 24:58.050
AND FOR THAT, I'M OUT.

25:03.070 --> 25:06.080
JUST LIKE MONEY, WHEN THERE'S
NOT ENOUGH BUYERS,

25:06.080 --> 25:08.068
MY MONEY BECOMES MORE VALUABLE,

25:08.068 --> 25:10.045
AND JUST LIKE REAL MONEY,

25:10.045 --> 25:12.083
YOU HAVE A DEPRECIATING ASSET
RIGHT NOW.

25:10.045 --> 25:12.083
RIGHT. RIGHT.

25:12.083 --> 25:14.062
SO UNLESS YOU GIVE ME
AN ANSWER RIGHT NOW,

25:14.062 --> 25:16.037
IT'S GOING UP TO 85%.

25:16.037 --> 25:18.055
(chuckles) 80%?

25:23.072 --> 25:24.077
SO, AGAIN, I THINK THAT

25:24.077 --> 25:26.058
THIS MARKET HAS
TREMENDOUS POTENTIAL.

25:26.058 --> 25:28.038
80% IS TOO MUCH.

25:29.083 --> 25:31.062
I CAN'T DO 80%.

25:31.062 --> 25:33.045
THEN I'M OUT.

25:38.077 --> 25:40.050
THERE GOES THE MONEY.

25:40.050 --> 25:41.077
(laughs)

25:41.077 --> 25:45.040
(Pat) I HAVE NO REGRETS,
TURNING DOWN DAYMOND'S OFFER.

25:45.040 --> 25:48.038
THE 80% WAS JUST OUT OF LINE.

25:48.038 --> 25:51.038
