27:00.050 --> 27:01.050
ALL RIGHT.

27:01.050 --> 27:05.033
(all chuckle)

27:05.033 --> 27:06.063
ONCE THESE HIT THE MARKET,

27:06.063 --> 27:09.045
NO ONE WILL WANT TO BE CAUGHT
WITHOUT THEIR TAIL LIGHTZ ON.

27:09.045 --> 27:11.053
TAIL LIGHTZ ARE
ATTACHABLE LIGHTED DESIGNS

27:11.053 --> 27:12.063
FOR JEAN POCKETS.

27:12.063 --> 27:15.058
ANYONE CAN EASILY ATTACH
OR DETACH TAIL LIGHTZ

27:15.058 --> 27:18.045
TO THE BACK POCKET
OF ANY JEANS, SHORTS,

27:18.045 --> 27:23.062
OR, HECK, EVEN YOUR HAT,
PURSE, OR BACKPACK.

27:23.062 --> 27:25.023
THERE ARE
TINY, STRONG MAGNETS

27:25.023 --> 27:27.020
ON THE BACK
OF EACH LIGHTED DESIGN,

27:27.020 --> 27:29.053
WHICH HOLD IT IN PLACE
NO MATTER WHAT YOU PUT IT ON.

27:29.053 --> 27:32.058
WE CAN TAILOR OUR DESIGNS
TOWARDS ALL AGE GROUPS.

27:32.058 --> 27:36.030
DESIGNS LIKE THE SMILEY FACE
AND SPORTS THEMES

27:36.030 --> 27:38.020
WILL APPEAL TOWARDS
YOUNG KIDS,

27:38.020 --> 27:39.058
AND OUR FUN PHRASE DESIGNS,

27:39.058 --> 27:44.058
LIKE "SASSY BRITCHES,"
"ROCK STAR," AND "DRAMA QUEEN,"

27:44.058 --> 27:47.067
WILL APPEAL TOWARDS
GIRLS AND WOMEN OF ALL AGES.

27:47.067 --> 27:50.058
THE POSSIBILITIES ARE
ENDLESS.

27:52.032 --> 27:54.032
MY PRODUCTS ARE CURRENTLY
IN THE DESIGN PHASE

27:54.032 --> 27:55.065
WITH WORKING PROTOTYPES.

27:55.065 --> 27:58.045
WITH YOUR PARTNERSHIP,
I WILL BE ABLE TO DESIGN

27:58.045 --> 28:00.053
SLIMMER RETAIL-READY PRODUCTS
AND PACKAGING...

27:58.045 --> 28:00.053
THANK YOU.

28:00.053 --> 28:02.058
SO THAT TAIL LIGHTZ WILL
SOON BE LIGHTING UP

28:02.058 --> 28:04.067
EVERY RETAIL STORE
ACROSS THE COUNTRY.

28:04.067 --> 28:08.028
SO WHO IS READY TO PARTNER
WITH AN EXPERIENCED INVENTOR

28:08.028 --> 28:09.065
AND LIGHT THINGS UP?

28:09.065 --> 28:11.040
WHO'S READY?
I'M READY.

28:11.040 --> 28:12.058
THAT'S IT? YOU'RE IN?

28:11.040 --> 28:12.058
THAT'S IT?

28:12.058 --> 28:14.022
ALL RIGHT. LET'S GO.

28:14.022 --> 28:15.055
I AM READY TO GO OUT.

28:15.055 --> 28:16.065
(Robert) OH. (laughs)

28:16.065 --> 28:17.065
(laughs)

28:17.065 --> 28:21.027
I'M OUT.

28:21.027 --> 28:22.045
SO, BARBARA,
YOU'RE REALLY OUT?

28:22.045 --> 28:24.067
YES. WOULD YOU LIKE
TO KNOW WHY?

28:22.045 --> 28:24.067
DO YOU WANT TO--

28:24.067 --> 28:26.018
DO YOU WANT TO MAKE
A SPEECH ABOUT WHY? SURE.

28:26.018 --> 28:27.067
I WOULDN'T MIND. YEAH.

28:26.018 --> 28:27.067
SURE.

28:27.067 --> 28:30.042
FIRST OFF, SITTING ON THIS
WOULD BE PAINFUL...

28:30.042 --> 28:32.027
YEP.

28:30.042 --> 28:32.027
ON THE BACK SEAT
OF YOUR PANTS.

28:32.027 --> 28:34.033
SECONDLY, I BET
THEY DON'T WASH WELL

28:34.033 --> 28:36.062
WHEN YOU MAKE THE MISTAKE
OF FORGETTING TO TAKE THEM OFF.

28:36.062 --> 28:41.027
THIRD, I THINK THE DESIGNS
ON THESE FEEL DATED TO ME.

28:41.027 --> 28:43.020
BUT OTHER THAN THAT,
I LOVE THE IDEA.

28:43.020 --> 28:46.023
(Robert and Mark laugh)

28:46.023 --> 28:48.047
GUYS, WHAT DO YOU HAVE
ON YOUR TUSH?

28:48.047 --> 28:49.047
SASSY BRITCHES.

28:49.047 --> 28:50.060
SASSY BRITCHES.

28:50.060 --> 28:53.027
WOULD YOU GO ON A DATE
WEARING "SASSY BRITCHES"?

28:53.027 --> 28:55.027
UM...

28:55.027 --> 28:57.020
YOU SEE, THAT'S
THE PROBLEM, RIGHT?

28:57.020 --> 28:59.018
YOU'VE GOT YOUR CORE AUDIENCE
RIGHT HERE,

28:59.018 --> 29:00.028
BUT DO YOU THINK
IT'S GOING TO CATCH ON

29:00.028 --> 29:03.038
AND CATCH FIRE
AND LIGHTEN ALL OF AMERICA?

29:03.038 --> 29:04.052
I JUST DON'T SEE IT.

29:04.052 --> 29:06.060
WELL, KEEP IN MIND THAT
THESE PROTOTYPES ARE BULKY.

29:06.060 --> 29:09.032
I REALIZE THAT, AND THAT'S
WHY I'M HERE TODAY.

29:09.032 --> 29:11.025
I NEED THE FUNDING TO GET
TO THAT NEXT LEVEL.

29:11.025 --> 29:12.030
THERE'S OTHER PRODUCTS

29:12.030 --> 29:14.048
LIKE THIS OUT THERE.

29:12.030 --> 29:14.048
THEY DO MAKE--

29:14.048 --> 29:16.050
I HAVE NOT SEEN
ANY OTHER PRODUCTS

29:16.050 --> 29:17.065
THAT COMBINE THE LIGHTING
AND THE DESIGN.

29:17.065 --> 29:19.060
YOU'VE NEVER SEEN
A BUTTON THAT GLOWS?

29:19.060 --> 29:22.050
NOT IN A-A PATCH,
WITH THE LIGHTING LIKE THIS,

29:22.050 --> 29:24.027
THAT ARE DETACHABLE
AND CAN BE REMOVED AND--

29:24.027 --> 29:25.053
BUT THERE'S NOTHING PROPRIETARY
ABOUT IT, RIGHT?

29:25.053 --> 29:28.027
IF I WANTED TO KNOCK IT OFF,
WHY COULDN'T I JUST GO

29:28.027 --> 29:30.055
AND GET THIS MANUFACTURED
AND COMPETE WITH YOU?

29:30.055 --> 29:33.025
BECAUSE THERE'S NOTHING
TO STOP ME FROM DOING IT.

29:33.025 --> 29:35.065
WELL, I HAVE
TWO PATENTS PENDING.

29:35.065 --> 29:37.043
AND WHAT ARE
YOUR PATENTS FOR?

29:37.043 --> 29:40.040
THE PATENTS ARE FOR
THE DETACHABLE LIGHTED DESIGN,

29:40.040 --> 29:43.023
AND THEN THE OTHER PATENT IS
FOR THE FASHION LINE

29:43.023 --> 29:44.063
THAT I CREATED, WHICH IS CALLED
TWINKLE CHEEKS.

29:44.063 --> 29:46.040
SO WHAT DO YOU DO
FOR A LIVING, KYLE?

29:46.040 --> 29:48.035
I'M A MR. MOM,
I'M AN ARTIST,

29:48.035 --> 29:49.050
AND I'M AN INVENTOR.

29:49.050 --> 29:52.027
OKAY, AND DOES YOUR WIFE
MAKE A LOT OF MONEY?

29:52.027 --> 29:54.030
MY WIFE, UH, HAS FINANCIALLY
SUPPORTED OUR FAMILY

29:54.030 --> 29:55.038
FOR 13 YEARS NOW.

29:55.038 --> 29:56.055
SHE'S WONDERFUL.

29:56.055 --> 29:58.030
SHE IS THE MOST AMAZING WOMAN
ANYBODY COULD ASK FOR.

29:58.030 --> 30:00.065
SO SHE'S BASICALLY FUNDING
YOUR GOAL TO HAVE ONE OF THESE

30:00.065 --> 30:01.065
WORK OUT FOR YOU.

30:00.065 --> 30:01.065
THAT'S RIGHT,

30:01.065 --> 30:03.060
AND I AM AT THE POINT
IN MY LIFE

30:03.060 --> 30:07.032
WHERE I JUST REALLY NEED
TO SUCCEED,

30:07.032 --> 30:09.035
SO THAT SHE DOESN'T HAVE
TO WORK SO HARD.

30:09.035 --> 30:12.022
OKAY, KYLE, THIS IS NOT GOING
TO BE THE ONE THAT SUCCEEDS.

30:12.022 --> 30:13.065
I THINK YOU'VE GOT
THAT MESSAGE LOUD AND CLEAR.

30:13.065 --> 30:15.043
WE'VE ALL SEEN THIS.

30:15.043 --> 30:17.030
THERE'S NOTHING PROPRIETARY
ABOUT IT.

30:17.030 --> 30:18.033
I'M OUT.

30:20.040 --> 30:22.032
I GOTTA TELL YA,
BARBARA'S RIGHT.

30:22.032 --> 30:23.037
IT LOOKS DATED.

30:25.030 --> 30:26.048
I'M OUT.

30:28.035 --> 30:31.030
I'VE SEEN TEN OF THESE
IN THE LAST YEAR

30:31.030 --> 30:34.033
THAT EITHER WERE ALREADY
ON THE MARKET

30:34.033 --> 30:35.042
OR ALREADY DOING SALES.

30:35.042 --> 30:36.045
I'M OUT.

30:39.043 --> 30:41.065
KYLE,
THE IMPORTANT THING IS,

30:41.065 --> 30:44.022
IT DOESN'T MATTER
HOW MANY TIMES YOU FAIL.

30:44.022 --> 30:46.023
ALL IT TAKES IS ONE,

30:46.023 --> 30:49.028
THEN EVERYBODY CAN CALL YOU
AN OVERNIGHT SUCCESS...

30:49.028 --> 30:50.055
(chuckles) THAT'S TRUE.

30:49.028 --> 30:50.055
SO DON'T QUIT...

30:50.055 --> 30:52.065
MM-HMM.

30:50.055 --> 30:52.065
BECAUSE WE'VE ALL BEEN
LAUGHED AT.

30:52.065 --> 30:54.030
I KNOW I'VE BEEN LAUGHED AT,

30:54.030 --> 30:57.018
AND MY BIGGEST HITS HAVE BEEN
THE ONES PEOPLE THOUGHT

30:57.018 --> 30:58.042
WERE MOST LIKELY TO FAIL.

30:58.042 --> 30:59.042
YOU ARE...

30:59.042 --> 31:00.042
I'M OUT.

31:00.042 --> 31:02.052
OKAY.
THANK YOU FOR YOUR TIME.

31:02.052 --> 31:03.052
(Daymond and Barbara)
THANK YOU.

31:02.052 --> 31:03.052
I APPRECIATE IT.

31:03.052 --> 31:05.032
GOOD LUCK, KYLE.

31:03.052 --> 31:05.032
THANK YOU.

31:08.027 --> 31:10.028
(Kyle) IT'S PRETTY HUMILIATING.

31:10.028 --> 31:11.038
I'M JUST KINDA WONDERING,
YOU KNOW,

31:11.038 --> 31:14.025
DID I MAKE THE RIGHT MOVE
IN TAKING IT HERE?

