BUT, YOU KNOW, YOU--
YOU CAN'T LIVE LIFE LIKE THAT.

31:16.032 --> 31:18.055
YOU JUST HAVE TO TRY
AND--AND KEEP ON GOING.

31:18.055 --> 31:20.052
THAT WIFE IS INCREDIBLE.

31:20.052 --> 31:22.018
EITHER THAT
OR HE'S A GOOD DAD,

31:22.018 --> 31:23.018
AND SHE'S SMART
FOR LETTING HIM

31:23.018 --> 31:24.030
KEEP ON DOING IT.

31:23.018 --> 31:24.030
THAT'S TRUE.

31:24.030 --> 31:25.035
HE'S HOME LOOKING
AFTER THE KIDS.

31:25.035 --> 31:27.032
THAT'S THE BEST JOB
IN THE WORLD.

31:27.032 --> 31:30.023
♪♪♪

31:38.017 --> 31:40.042
NEXT UP IS MEGAN CUMMINS,

31:40.042 --> 31:43.040
WHO HAS A CHEEKY TWISTTO A COMMON PRODUCT.

31:56.038 --> 31:58.020
HI.
MY NAME IS MEGAN CUMMINS.

31:58.020 --> 32:00.003
MY COMPANY IS YOU SMELL,

32:00.003 --> 32:02.008
AND I'M SEEKING
A $55,000 INVESTMENT

32:02.008 --> 32:04.045
IN EXCHANGE FOR 20%
OF THE COMPANY.

32:04.045 --> 32:07.007
YOU SMELL IS
A NEW LUXURY SOAP BRAND

32:07.007 --> 32:08.010
THAT'S A BREATH
OF FRESH AIR

32:08.010 --> 32:10.033
IN AN OFTENTIMES SNOOTY
MARKETPLACE.

32:10.033 --> 32:14.013
IT HAS DELICIOUS FRAGRANCES
AND A VIBRANT PERSONALITY.

32:14.013 --> 32:15.040
YOU SMELL STARTED OUT
AS A CLASS PROJECT

32:15.040 --> 32:16.043
BACK IN COLLEGE.

32:16.043 --> 32:18.018
I WAS TAKING
A PACKAGE DESIGN CLASS,

32:18.018 --> 32:21.013
AND I HAD FREE REIN TO DEVELOP
ANY PRODUCT I WANTED.

32:21.013 --> 32:23.045
I WANTED TO DEVELOP SOMETHING
THAT HAD PERSONALITY,

32:23.045 --> 32:26.017
AND WHAT INSTANTLY CAME
TO MIND WAS YOU SMELL.

32:26.017 --> 32:28.037
I DIDN'T WANT TO BE BLINDED
BY, UM, EXCITEMENT,

32:28.037 --> 32:31.043
SO I DECIDED TO DO
A TRIAL RUN TO TEST THE MARKET.

32:31.043 --> 32:34.037
I HAD ABOUT 1,200 BARS MADE
IN 2 CUSTOM FRAGRANCES--

32:34.037 --> 32:37.000
LEMON VERBENA
AND LAVENDER MINT.

32:37.000 --> 32:38.010
UM, I BROUGHT YOU ALL
SOME SAMPLES,

32:38.010 --> 32:39.027
SO YOU CAN SMELL THEM.

32:39.027 --> 32:42.040
SO LOOK AT THIS. IT SAYS,
"YOU SMELL" ON THE FRONT,

32:42.040 --> 32:44.045
AND YOU FLIP IT AROUND,
AND IT SAYS, "LEMON."

32:44.045 --> 32:46.010
YOU SMELL LIKE A LEMON,
BARBARA.

32:44.045 --> 32:46.010
(chuckles)

32:46.010 --> 32:47.028
"LIKE A LEMON."

32:46.010 --> 32:47.028
IT'S CUTE.

32:47.028 --> 32:49.027
SINCE I HAVEN'T OPENED,
UH, MY DOORS YET

32:49.027 --> 32:52.022
TO ACTUALLY HAVE A REVENUE,
I HAVE TESTED THE MARKET.

32:52.022 --> 32:53.033
I ACTUALLY TOLD
A FEW BLOGS--

32:53.033 --> 32:55.033
OH, SO YOU HAVEN'T SOLD
ANY OF YOU SMELL YET?

32:55.033 --> 32:57.035
NO, I'M STILL PRE-VENTURE,
ACTUALLY.

32:57.035 --> 33:00.013
SO YOU HAVE BARS JUST SITTING
IN A WAREHOUSE OR WHAT?

33:00.013 --> 33:02.025
NO, ACTUALLY I HAD THOSE MADE
AND ALREADY GOT RID OF THEM,

33:02.025 --> 33:04.002
SENDING THEM OUT
TO DIFFERENT COMPANIES,

33:04.002 --> 33:06.022
AND THEN ALMOST OVERNIGHT
IT ENDED UP GOING INTERNATIONAL,

33:06.022 --> 33:08.017
YOU KNOW--NEW YORK,
L.A., AND CANADA, AUSTRALIA--

33:08.017 --> 33:09.045
DID YOU SELL THEM,
OR YOU GAVE THEM AWAY?

33:09.045 --> 33:11.015
I DID SELL THEM,
'CAUSE I WANTED TO SEE

33:11.015 --> 33:13.017
HOW MUCH PEOPLE WERE WILLING
TO PAY FOR THEM.

33:13.017 --> 33:14.045
AND WHAT DID YOU LEARN?

33:13.017 --> 33:14.045
AND WHAT--YEAH.

33:14.045 --> 33:16.022
WELL, PEOPLE WERE
SELLING THEM,

33:16.022 --> 33:19.013
SURPRISINGLY,
FOR BETWEEN $7 TO $12 A BAR,

33:19.013 --> 33:21.007
BUT I ALSO FOUND THAT
THERE WERE A LOT OF COMPANIES,

33:21.007 --> 33:23.038
SOME VERY BIG NAMES,
THAT, UM, ACTUALLY WANTED IT

33:23.038 --> 33:25.027
TO BE MORE LIKE
$4.50, $5.00.

33:25.027 --> 33:26.028
SO WHAT KIND OF NAMES?

33:26.028 --> 33:28.003
WHEN YOU SAY BIG NAMES,
WHO ARE THEY?

33:28.003 --> 33:30.010
THE BIGGEST ONE WOULD BE
URBAN OUTFITTERS.

33:30.010 --> 33:32.003
THEY ASKED, YOU KNOW,

33:32.003 --> 33:33.025
HOW FAST I COULD HAVE
STUFF MADE,

33:33.025 --> 33:34.032
IN WHAT QUANTITIES,

33:34.032 --> 33:36.007
AND THEN WHAT
THE PRICE POINT WOULD BE.

33:36.007 --> 33:38.045
MEGAN, WHAT--WHAT IS THIS?
IS THIS A PAPER PRODUCT,

33:38.045 --> 33:40.010
A PAPER VERSION OF THE SOAP?

33:38.045 --> 33:40.010
YEAH, IT--IT'S ACTUALLY--

33:40.010 --> 33:41.023
IT'S PAPER SOAP,

33:41.023 --> 33:43.015
UM, SO IT'S SMALLER
THAN A LITTLE PACKET OF GUM.

33:43.015 --> 33:44.037
YOU CAN FIT IT
IN YOUR PURSE, YOUR POCKET.

33:44.037 --> 33:46.005
I'VE NEVER SEEN
THAT BEFORE.

33:46.005 --> 33:47.030
IT'S SOMETHING
THAT WOULD BE AN--YOU KNOW,

33:47.030 --> 33:48.040
AN IMPULSE BUY
AT A REGISTER.

33:48.040 --> 33:50.008
AND YOU SELL IT FOR...

33:50.008 --> 33:54.012
THE SOAP BARS ARE GOING TO BE
ROUGHLY ABOUT 80 CENTS.

33:54.012 --> 33:56.000
RETAIL, THAT WOULD BE
ABOUT $2.25.

33:56.000 --> 33:57.040
NOT BAD MARGINS.
NOT BAD MARGINS.

33:57.040 --> 33:59.008
GREAT MARGINS.
I LIKE IT.

33:59.008 --> 34:01.018
MEGAN, IF I INVEST
IN YOUR COMPANY HERE--

34:01.018 --> 34:03.035
I'M A SLAVE DRIVER, RIGHT,
AND I DEMAND A LOT,

34:03.035 --> 34:04.035
SO I'D BE INVEST--

34:03.035 --> 34:04.035
OH, MY GOODNESS.

34:04.035 --> 34:06.000
YOU'RE GONNA LOVE ME.

34:06.000 --> 34:07.008
(Mark and Barbara laugh)

34:07.008 --> 34:08.023
I'M PROBABLY
THE MOST TENACIOUS PERSON

34:08.023 --> 34:09.047
YOU'RE EVER GOING TO MEET.

34:09.047 --> 34:11.022
I MEAN,
WITH YOUR BUSINESS SKILLS

34:11.022 --> 34:14.022
AND, YOU KNOW, YOUR CONNECTIONS
AND FINANCIAL BACKING,

34:14.022 --> 34:17.003
COMBINED WITH MY TENACITY
AND MY ADDICTION TO CAFFEINE,

34:17.003 --> 34:18.003
UM, IT'S UNSTOPPABLE.

34:17.003 --> 34:18.003
(sharks laugh)

34:18.003 --> 34:19.020
ADDICTION TO CAFFEINE.

34:18.003 --> 34:19.020
(laughs)

34:19.020 --> 34:21.000
HAVE YOU PLANNED OUT WHAT YOU
WOULD DO WITH THE $50,000?

34:21.000 --> 34:22.040
IT'S ACTUALLY JUST
GOING PRIMARILY

34:22.040 --> 34:24.007
TO BUILDING THE PRODUCT.

34:24.007 --> 34:27.005
DO YOU HAVE AN ORDER FROM
SOMEBODY TO SELL IT TO THEM?

34:27.005 --> 34:28.047
UM, I-I DON'T HAVE
ACTUAL P.O.s,

34:28.047 --> 34:30.018
UM, 'CAUSE Y--I DON'T WANT
TO PROMISE SOMETHING

34:30.018 --> 34:32.033
AND THEN SOMETHING FALL THROUGH
AND NOT BE ABLE TO GET IT.

34:32.033 --> 34:34.027
SO, MEGAN, UM...

34:37.000 --> 34:39.022
I HAVE TO ADMIRE YOUR TENACITY,

34:39.022 --> 34:42.036
BUT THIS IS NOT REALLY
A BUSINESS I'M INTERESTED IN.

34:42.036 --> 34:44.036
I'M OUT.

34:46.047 --> 34:48.027
YOU'RE IN
A BRUTALLY COMPETITIVE MARKET.

34:48.027 --> 34:51.012
I MEAN, ANYBODY, INCLUDING ME,
IF I WANTED TO,

34:51.012 --> 34:53.033
COULD FIND A MEGAN
AND GET INTO THE SOAP BUSINESS,

34:53.033 --> 34:55.033
SO THE ONLY THING
OF VALUE HERE IS A BRAND,

34:55.033 --> 34:56.043
WHICH IS UNPROVEN YET.

34:56.043 --> 34:58.013
GOOD LUCK TO YOU,

34:58.013 --> 34:59.035
AND I'M IMPRESSED
WITH YOUR PRESENTATION,

34:59.035 --> 35:02.022
BUT IT DOESN'T MAKE IT EASY
FOR ME TO SMELL THE MONEY.

35:02.022 --> 35:03.038
I'M OUT.

35:04.042 --> 35:06.027
(inhales deeply)

35:08.037 --> 35:12.035
ALL RIGHT, MEGAN.
I'M--I'M TEETER-TOTTERING.

35:12.035 --> 35:14.015
I MEAN, WHAT MAKES YOU
THE PERSON

35:14.015 --> 35:17.028
TO TAKE THIS
FROM CONCEPT AND DESIGN

35:17.028 --> 35:19.042
ALL THE WAY
THROUGH TO SUCCESS?

35:19.042 --> 35:22.042
UM, WELL, I GUESS
THE FIRST, UM, EXAMPLE

35:22.042 --> 35:25.025
WOULD BE THAT I DECIDED THAT
I WAS GONNA GIVE IT A GO,

35:25.025 --> 35:28.027
AND IN ABOUT A MONTH,
I HAD INTERNATIONAL PRESS.

35:28.027 --> 35:30.000
YOU KNOW, I HAD MAGAZINES
IN THE STATES.

35:30.000 --> 35:31.017
"TATLER" IN THE U.K. WROTE
ABOUT ME.

35:31.017 --> 35:32.038
BUT, YOU KNOW,
THAT'S SHORT-LIVED.

35:32.038 --> 35:35.000
IT DOESN'T MEAN YOU'RE GONNA
CONTINUOUSLY GET THAT PRESS,

35:35.000 --> 35:37.015
AND IT DOESN'T MEAN YOU CAN
ALWAYS CONVERT IT TO SALES.

35:37.015 --> 35:38.037
WHAT--WHAT SKILLS
DO YOU HAVE

35:38.037 --> 35:40.005
THAT ARE GONNA GIVE US
CONFIDENCE,

35:40.005 --> 35:41.042
OR GIVE ME CONFIDENCE TO SAY,
"YOU KNOW WHAT?

35:41.042 --> 35:45.022
ONCE WE GET PAST THE HYPE,
WE CAN DELIVER."

35:48.028 --> 35:50.028
UH, THERE'S NOTHING
THAT CAN STOP ME.

35:50.028 --> 35:52.012
TRUST ME.
IF YOU TEACH ME ROPES,

35:52.012 --> 35:53.012
AND YOU TELL ME
WHAT I NEED TO DO,

35:53.012 --> 35:54.025
I WILL GET IT DONE,

35:54.025 --> 35:55.045
AND YOU DON'T EVEN HAVE
TO THINK ABOUT IT AGAIN.

35:55.045 --> 35:57.022
THAT'S WHAT GONNA BE SO GREAT
ABOUT WORKING WITH ME.

35:57.022 --> 35:58.022
YOU DON'T HAVE
TO KEEP TELLING ME

35:58.022 --> 35:59.033
OVER AND OVER
AND OVER AGAIN.

35:59.033 --> 36:01.038
LIKE, I KNOW WHAT HAS
TO BE DONE, AND I DO IT.

36:01.038 --> 36:03.040
I--THERE'S JUST SOMETHING
IN MY BLOOD. (chuckles)

36:03.040 --> 36:05.000
I'M SURE YOU GUYS
UNDERSTAND IT.

36:05.000 --> 36:06.023
(laughs)

36:05.000 --> 36:06.023
I... (chuckles)

36:09.048 --> 36:11.012
SO?

36:12.037 --> 36:17.003
SO FOR $55,000 FOR 20%,

36:17.003 --> 36:18.042
WE HAVE A DEAL?

36:18.042 --> 36:21.035
NO. JUST WAIT
A MINUTE THERE.

36:24.023 --> 36:28.008
♪♪♪

36:32.013 --> 36:35.085
TWO SHARKS ARE OUT, AND MEGANHAS ONE OFFER FROM MARK.

36:35.085 --> 36:40.005
SO FOR $55,000 FOR 20%,

36:40.005 --> 36:41.093
WE HAVE A DEAL?

36:41.093 --> 36:44.088
NO. JUST WAIT
A MINUTE THERE.

36:46.090 --> 36:48.072
YOU'RE A TOTAL SURPRISE.

36:48.072 --> 36:50.068
I WROTE YOU OFF
THE MINUTE YOU WALKED IN.

36:50.068 --> 36:53.007
RIGHT AWAY, "HERE COMES
A BLONDE BOMBSHELL,"

36:53.007 --> 36:54.095
BUT THE MORE YOU TALK,
THE MORE I'M CONVINCED

36:54.095 --> 36:56.013
THAT YOU'RE
A REAL KILLER.

36:56.013 --> 36:58.007
THANK YOU. THAT MEANS A LOT
COMING FROM YOU.

36:58.007 --> 36:59.008
BUT--

36:59.008 --> 37:01.083
HERE COMES
HER BLOODSUCKING OFFER.

37:03.095 --> 37:07.068
MEGAN, LISTEN TO ME
JUST A MINUTE, ALL RIGHT?

37:07.068 --> 37:09.088
EVERY SINGLE ENTREPRENEUR

37:09.088 --> 37:13.017
THAT I'VE INVESTED IN
ON THIS SHOW IS MAKING MONEY.

37:13.017 --> 37:14.095
WHY IS THAT?

37:14.095 --> 37:18.077
BECAUSE I WORK MY BUNS OFF
MAKING SURE THEY'RE A SUCCESS.

37:18.077 --> 37:22.093
WHEN THEY CALL ME,
THEY FIND ME IMMEDIATELY.

37:22.093 --> 37:25.075
IF YOUR SOAP IS SUCCESSFUL,

37:25.075 --> 37:27.068
IT'S GONNA TAKE A LOT MORE MONEY
THAN $50,000,

37:27.068 --> 37:29.002
SO YOU'RE NOT IN HERE
ASKING FOR ENOUGH.

37:29.002 --> 37:32.098
BUT I'M GONNA GIVE YOU
THE... $55,000,

37:32.098 --> 37:35.085
BUT I MUST TAKE...

37:35.085 --> 37:38.015
40% OF YOUR BUSINESS.

37:40.077 --> 37:42.008
BECAUSE THE TRUTH
OF THE MATTER IS,

37:42.008 --> 37:44.092
I HAVE TO MAKE A RETURN,

37:44.092 --> 37:48.013
AND I ALSO NEED A DIME
FOR EVERY BAR YOU SELL.

37:52.010 --> 37:54.010
SO IF YOU'LL GIVE ME
A DIME A BAR

37:54.010 --> 37:57.075
AND YOU'LL GIVE ME 40%
OF YOUR BUSINESS FOR $55,000,

37:57.075 --> 38:00.010
I WOULD LOVE TO BE
YOUR PARTNER,

38:00.010 --> 38:03.083
AND YOU'LL JUST BE
ANOTHER SUCCESS STORY.

38:05.013 --> 38:06.095
OKAY.

38:06.095 --> 38:08.013
I'M GONNA START TO CRY.

38:06.095 --> 38:08.013
AND I'D LOVE TO HAVE
AN ANSWER NOW.

38:08.013 --> 38:09.085
I--REALLY, I'M SO MOVED.

38:08.013 --> 38:09.085
DON'T BE--YOU--

38:09.085 --> 38:11.007
OH, HUSH. (chuckles)

38:11.007 --> 38:13.092
ALL THAT WARM AND FUZZY STUFF
CAME OUT TO A BLOODSUCKING OFFER

38:13.092 --> 38:15.078
OF 40% OF YOUR COMPANY.

38:16.093 --> 38:20.098
THIS IS A NO-BRAINER.
MY OFFER IS CLEARLY BETTER.

38:20.098 --> 38:22.090
(inhales deeply and sighs)
OH, MY GOODNESS.

38:22.090 --> 38:24.073
MEGAN, I CAN SMELL
THE BLOOD IN THE WATER.

38:24.073 --> 38:27.072
YOU'VE GOT BARBARA.
YOU'VE GOT, UH, MARK CIRCLING.

38:27.072 --> 38:29.008
YOU CAN ALSO SMELL
THE LEMONS, TOO.

38:29.008 --> 38:30.070
I CAN SMELL THE LEMONS...

38:29.008 --> 38:30.070
(chuckles)

38:30.070 --> 38:32.078
AND, UH, MOST IMPORTANTLY,
I SMELL YOUR DRIVE.

38:32.078 --> 38:33.095
I DIDN'T WRITE YOU OFF.

38:33.095 --> 38:34.097
THANK YOU. (chuckles)

38:33.095 --> 38:34.097
I DON'T MAKE A JUDGMENT

38:34.097 --> 38:36.090
ON HOW PEOPLE LOOK,
UNLIKE BARBARA...

38:36.090 --> 38:39.002
(chuckles)

38:36.090 --> 38:39.002
UH...

38:39.002 --> 38:40.005
DO YOU HAVE YOUR OWN JOB?

38:40.005 --> 38:41.075
I WORK, UM, FOR MYSELF
INDEPENDENTLY

38:41.075 --> 38:42.090
AS A GRAPHIC DESIGNER.

38:42.090 --> 38:44.070
DO YOU WANT TO DO
THIS FULL-TIME?

38:44.070 --> 38:46.003
I--THAT'S WHY I'M HERE.
(chuckles)

38:46.003 --> 38:47.077
I THINK IT'S
A FANTASTIC PRODUCT.

38:47.077 --> 38:48.077
I THINK IT'S
A GREAT BRAND...

38:48.077 --> 38:49.077
THANK YOU.

38:49.077 --> 38:52.070
BUT MY CONCERN IS,

38:52.070 --> 38:55.070
ARE YOU GONNA QUIT
YOUR OTHER JOB?

38:55.070 --> 38:58.070
YEAH, I-I PRETTY MUCH
ALREADY HAVE. (chuckles)

38:58.070 --> 39:00.095
WELL, PRETTY MUCH IS NOT
ALL OF IT.

39:00.095 --> 39:03.087
YES. YES. ALREADY HAVE.
IT'S SAID AND DONE. THIS IS--

39:03.087 --> 39:04.087
HOW WILL YOU--HOW WILL
YOU SUPPORT YOURSELF, THOUGH?

39:03.087 --> 39:04.087
THIS IS MY LIFE NOW.

39:04.087 --> 39:06.010
SO THIS IS 100%?

39:04.087 --> 39:06.010
I'M SORRY?

39:06.010 --> 39:07.010
HOW WILL YOU SUPPORT YOURSELF
WHEN YOU QUIT YOUR OTHER JOB?

39:07.010 --> 39:08.088
I'VE BEEN A LITTLE CHIPMUNK.

39:08.088 --> 39:12.013
I'VE BEEN STOWING THINGS AWAY
SO THAT I COULD MAKE THIS JUMP.

39:12.013 --> 39:14.068
MEGAN, LOOK, I'VE HAD
A TON OF EXPERIENCE

39:14.068 --> 39:16.013
SUPPORTING ENTREPRENEURS.

39:16.013 --> 39:19.087
I KNOW WHAT IT'S LIKE TO BE
AN ENTREPRENEUR AND STARVE.

39:19.087 --> 39:21.070
I KNOW WHAT IT'S LIKE
TO HAVE ALL YOUR DREAMS

39:21.070 --> 39:23.012
JUST SITTING THERE
RIGHT IN FRONT OF YOU,

39:23.012 --> 39:24.015
AND YOU'RE JUST
KNOWING THAT

39:24.015 --> 39:26.000
IF I JUST HAD SOMEBODY
WHO COULD HELP ME

39:26.000 --> 39:27.013
AND WHO HAD BEEN
THERE BEFORE,

39:27.013 --> 39:29.000
THEY COULD GET ME
OVER THE TOP.

39:29.000 --> 39:30.007
THAT'S WHO I AM.

39:30.007 --> 39:31.093
THAT'S WHY
I'M SITTING HERE,

39:31.093 --> 39:35.012
AND THAT'S WHY I LIKE TO GET
INVOLVED WITH PEOPLE LIKE YOU.

39:37.012 --> 39:39.078
HERE'S WHAT I THINK
YOU NEED TO DO.

39:39.078 --> 39:41.092
I SMELL SUCCESS IN YOU.

39:41.092 --> 39:44.010
THIS IS PURELY
AN INVESTMENT IN YOU.

39:44.010 --> 39:46.092
I THINK WHAT YOU NEED IS,
YOU NEED SOME CASH FLOW

39:46.092 --> 39:48.080
TO GIVE YOU THE FREEDOM
TO MAKE THE RIGHT DECISIONS.

39:46.092 --> 39:48.080
SHE IS SO FAR--

39:48.080 --> 39:50.097
NO, WAIT, WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.
YOU ARE SO FAR FROM DESPERATE...

39:50.097 --> 39:52.077
SO LET ME--

39:50.097 --> 39:52.077
YOU SHOULD JUST BE LAUGHING
AT THAT.

39:52.077 --> 39:55.015
NO, NO, BUT, MEGAN,
MARK ISN'T LISTENING.

39:55.015 --> 39:57.012
HE'S HEARING HALF THE STORY.

39:57.012 --> 39:59.093
I THINK WHAT THE OFFER
NEEDS TO BE IS,

39:59.093 --> 40:03.010
THE BUSINESS NEEDS
$55,000 FOR THE 20%,

40:03.010 --> 40:05.005
BUT I THINK YOU NEED
A SALARY ALONG THE WAY

40:05.005 --> 40:06.097
IN THE FIRST YEAR.

40:06.097 --> 40:09.097
YOU HAVE TAKEN THIS AND DONE
A LOT OF AMAZING THINGS.

40:09.097 --> 40:11.013
THAT'S WHY YOU'RE GETTING
SO MUCH INTEREST.

40:11.013 --> 40:16.000
MY OFFER WOULD BE TO PAY YOU
THE $55,000 FOR THE 20%,

40:16.000 --> 40:18.075
BUT PAY YOU ANOTHER $50,000
FOR YOU TO LIVE

40:18.075 --> 40:20.090
IN THE FIRST 12 MONTHS,
SO YOU HAVE THE FREEDOM...

40:20.090 --> 40:22.078
(chuckles)

40:20.090 --> 40:22.078
TO MAKE THE RIGHT DECISIONS

40:22.078 --> 40:24.068
AND GROW THE BUSINESS...

40:22.078 --> 40:24.068
(Kevin) YOU GUYS ARE ALL NUTS.

40:24.068 --> 40:25.072
'CAUSE THAT'S WHAT
I BELIEVE IN.

40:24.068 --> 40:25.072
THIS ISN'T GOLD BARS.

40:25.072 --> 40:28.075
THIS IS SOAP. THIS IS CRAZY.

40:29.088 --> 40:31.078
PICK AN OFFER.

40:34.083 --> 40:38.017
I'M GONNA EDIT MY OFFER
FOR YOU, ALL RIGHT?

40:39.075 --> 40:44.098
I'LL GIVE YOU THE $55,000
FOR THE 30%.

40:44.098 --> 40:47.000
MEGAN, BEFORE--

40:47.000 --> 40:49.002
MEGAN--

40:47.000 --> 40:49.002
WAIT. LET ME JUST ADD
SOMETHING HERE.

40:49.002 --> 40:51.077
IN THE BIG PICTURE
OF THINGS, RIGHT,

40:51.077 --> 40:52.090
IT'S NOT ABOUT THE CASH.

40:52.090 --> 40:54.082
IT'S ABOUT WHO'S GONNA GIVE
YOU THE SUPPORT.

40:54.082 --> 40:57.087
I CAN MAKE AVAILABLE TIME
AND EXPERIENCE AND ACCESS

40:57.087 --> 40:58.098
TO MY OTHER COMPANIES
AS WELL.

40:58.098 --> 41:02.013
I THINK THE MONEY
IN THE FIRST YEAR IS IMPORTANT.

41:02.013 --> 41:03.072
RIGHT NOW IT'S ABOUT SURVIVAL.

41:03.072 --> 41:04.078
I THINK A LITTLE EXTRA CASH

41:04.078 --> 41:07.015
IS GONNA HELP YOU
GO ON THE RIGHT PATH,

41:07.015 --> 41:08.097
AND I BELIEVE IN YOU.
YOU'RE GONNA GET THERE.

41:08.097 --> 41:11.000
(Barbara) BUT IT'S NOT
AN IMPORTANT CARD HERE.

41:11.000 --> 41:12.017
YOU KNOW WHAT'S
AN IMPORTANT CARD HERE?

41:12.017 --> 41:14.093
THAT YOU GET LINED UP
WITH THE RIGHT DISTRIBUTOR.

41:14.093 --> 41:17.002
YOU'RE NOT GONNA BE
SUCCESSFUL

41:17.002 --> 41:18.070
BECAUSE OF
OTHER PEOPLE'S SUCCESS.

41:18.070 --> 41:20.075
YOU'RE GONNA BE SUCCESSFUL
BECAUSE OF YOUR OWN SUCCESS.

41:20.075 --> 41:23.015
BUT LET ME TELL YOU, WOMEN WORK
HARDER, AND YOU KNOW IT.

41:23.015 --> 41:24.015
OHH.

41:23.015 --> 41:24.015
I WORK CIRCLES
AROUND THIS GUY.

41:24.015 --> 41:26.002
OH, PLEASE.

41:24.015 --> 41:26.002
OH, BOY.

41:26.002 --> 41:27.010
ABSOLUTELY.

41:26.002 --> 41:27.010
REALLY?

41:27.010 --> 41:28.087
I-I GOT HERE
BECAUSE I DIDN'T WORK?

41:28.087 --> 41:29.093
NO. WOMEN WORK HARDER
THAN MEN.

41:29.093 --> 41:31.005
(imitates violin)

41:29.093 --> 41:31.005
(chuckles)

41:31.005 --> 41:32.098
PUT ONE WOMAN AGAINST A MAN
IN ANY SITUATION...

41:32.098 --> 41:34.090
PLEASE.

41:32.098 --> 41:34.090
SHE WILL OUTWORK
THE GUY ANYTIME.

41:34.090 --> 41:35.098
GIRL POWER.

41:34.090 --> 41:35.098
YOU KNOW WHY?

41:35.098 --> 41:37.077
ALL RIGHT.
ENOUGH, ENOUGH, ENOUGH.

41:35.098 --> 41:37.077
(laughs)

41:37.077 --> 41:39.077
MEGAN, YOU GOTTA MAKE
A CALL.

41:39.077 --> 41:41.070
WHAT ARE YOU GOING TO DO?

41:44.073 --> 41:47.007
I LOVE ALL THE OFFERS,
AND I LOVE ALL OF YOU GUYS.

41:47.007 --> 41:49.088
UM, BARBARA, I'VE ALWAYS WANTED
YOU TO BE MY BUSINESS MOM...

41:49.088 --> 41:54.017
(chuckles) BUT STARTING OUT
THIS FIRST COUPLE OF YEARS,

41:54.017 --> 41:56.080
MONEY IS CRUCIAL.

41:56.080 --> 41:58.078
I THINK I'M GOING TO GO
WITH ROBERT'S DEAL.

41:58.078 --> 41:59.078
OHH.

41:59.078 --> 42:01.090
OH, GREAT DECISION.

42:01.090 --> 42:03.088
IS THAT A FINAL DECISION,
MEGAN?

42:03.088 --> 42:04.088
(inhales deeply)

42:04.088 --> 42:05.088
YES.

42:05.088 --> 42:07.068
I WOULD--
I WOULD THINK TWICE.

42:07.068 --> 42:09.068
I WOULD THINK TWICE
ABOUT THAT FINAL.

42:09.068 --> 42:11.012
THANK YOU. THANK YOU.
(laughs)

42:11.012 --> 42:13.013
CONGRATULATIONS. GREAT JOB.

42:13.013 --> 42:15.000
YOU MADE A MISTAKE, MEGAN.

42:15.000 --> 42:16.092
(chuckles)

42:15.000 --> 42:16.092
(Kevin) ALL OF THAT,

42:16.092 --> 42:18.085
AND SHE JUST TOOK THE MONEY.

42:18.085 --> 42:20.098
IT MAKES ME FEEL
WARM AND FUZZY INSIDE.

42:18.085 --> 42:20.098
(Mark) WOW.

42:22.073 --> 42:24.005
CHOOSING BETWEEN
THOSE THREE AMAZING DEALS

42:24.005 --> 42:27.002
WAS REALLY DIFFICULT,
BUT HAVING THAT EXTRA MONEY

42:27.002 --> 42:28.085
IS REALLY WHAT HELPED TIP
THE SCALES,

42:28.085 --> 42:29.098
UM, AND I THINK
ROBERT'S GOING TO BE

42:29.098 --> 42:32.012
A GREAT BUSINESS PARTNER FOR ME.

